          <header>
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">AI21 Labs Jamba API 2026: The Mamba-Transformer Hybrid at Production Scale</h1>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4">
              <time datetime="2026-06-11">June 11, 2026</time>
